ad/1459852/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1459852/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"8f09b86157c65fc7643c037349e1dddb33b45cf1","tid":1459625,"uid":293698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T23:49:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8baec52f158234b88b0abaff044c213fc92806b7","tid":1459625,"uid":202889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T23:49:17.000Z","msg":"借po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n解決各國旅客無法離港的各種方法 (Ver. 1)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1459870\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1459870</a>"},{"pid":"5a1a64d80612ae6a7fd5eba765a428bf55cc62c5","tid":1459625,"uid":187538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:10:14.000Z","msg":"幾時有共識過無需要再BLACK BLOC?<br />\n你敢唔敢係明知機場高清無死角CCTV下便服但唔帶口罩?<br />\nblack bloc 保護自己之餘又保護到人地<br />\n<br />\n點解唔著黑衫<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1459798\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1459798</a><br />\n<br />\n大撚鑊 有手足唸埋啲屎橋會害鳩死我地啊！全世界一定同我著black block！！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1459696\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1459696</a><br />\n<br />\n有冒用律師身份開post叫人唔好著黑衫<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1459584\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1459584</a>"}]}